{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnusedDecidableInType.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnusedDecidableInType.unusedDecidableInTypeLinter\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnusedDecidableInType</span>.<span class=\"name\">unusedDecidableInTypeLinter</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.Linter\">Linter</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Enables the 'unused `Decidable*` in type' linter, which lints against `Decidable*` instance\nhypotheses in the types of theorems which are not used in the remainder of the type, and could\ntherefore be replaced with `classical` in the proof.\n\nThis linter fires only on theorems. (This includes `lemma`s and `instance`s of `Prop` classes.)\nThe constants recognised as `Decidable*` are `Decidable`, `DecidablePred`, `DecidableRel`,\n`DecidableEq`, `DecidableLE`, and `DecidableLT`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnusedDecidableInType.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnusedDecidableInType.unusedDecidableInTypeLinter","kind":"def","line":276,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnusedDecidableInType.unusedDecidableInTypeLinter","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnusedDecidableInType.lean#L276-L298"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnusedDecidableInType.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.linter.extra.unusedDecidableInType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">unusedDecidableInType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Enables the 'unused `Decidable*` in type' linter, which lints against `Decidable*` instance\nhypotheses in the types of theorems which are not used in the remainder of the type, and could\ntherefore be replaced with `classical` in the proof.\n\nThis linter fires only on theorems. (This includes `lemma`s and `instance`s of `Prop` classes.)\nThe constants recognised as `Decidable*` are `Decidable`, `DecidablePred`, `DecidableRel`,\n`DecidableEq`, `DecidableLE`, and `DecidableLT`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnusedDecidableInType.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.linter.extra.unusedDecidableInType","kind":"opaque","line":111,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.linter.extra.unusedDecidableInType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnusedDecidableInType.lean#L111-L125"}}],"imports":["Lean.Linter.Basic","Lean.Linter.Util","Lean.Meta.ForEachExpr","Lean.Meta.Sorry","Lean.PrivateName","Lean.Server.InfoUtils"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnusedDecidableInType"}